mawn : Non-paging, search-friendly man page system

    mawn [CATEGORY]... [SEARCH TERM]

Mawn is designed to help you find what you're actually looking for, fast, and in easy-to-understand terminology, without taking over your console. This includes providing not only explanations of flags, syntax, and purpose, but also extensive catalogs of recipes and general help administrating your system.

To use mawn, type what you're looking for. If there's a specific page or category for that keyword, mawn will use that, but if not, it will do a search. This is easiest to understand by looking at some of the provided examples.
